data.description: Exquisite Residence on a Sprawling Half-Acre, solar powered!, amidst tranquil neighborhood. Solid concrete block construction w/ lovely upgrades. Open & airy w/ soaring ceilings and luxury vinyl flooring. Split floor plan offering privacy & harmony. Owner's suite beckons w/ garden tub & walk-in closet, creating an oasis of comfort & relaxation. Open kitchen adorned w/ upgraded SS appliances. Dedicated fenced pool area w/ expansive deck promises endless fun & rejuvenation on sun-drenched Florida days. Charming matching shed for extra storage. Updated HVAC & water heater. Hurricane shutters. No HOA liberates you to curate your lifestyle to perfection. Boats & trailers welcome! The list of awesome goes on, inviting you to an idyllic country existence mere minutes from shopping, dining, & I95
